1. Molim vas da *ubijete* svetlo pre spavanja. (Please turn off the light before sleeping.)
2. Oni su želeli da *ubiju* vreme dok čekaju autobus. (They wanted to kill time while waiting for the bus.)
3. Ne želim da mi *ubijete* nadu. (I don't want you to kill my hope.)
4. Ako *ubijete* ovu biljku, neću vam dati drugu. (If you kill this plant, I won't give you another one.)
5. Znao je da će ga on *ubiti* ako se ne predaju. (He knew that he would be killed by him if he didn't surrender.)
6. Nemoj da me *ubiješ* ovom bukom. (Don't kill me with this noise.)
7. Uspeli su da *ubiju* zločinca nakon kraće potrage. (They managed to kill the criminal after a short pursuit.)
8. Zamolio je da ga *ubiju* brzo i bezbolno. (He asked them to kill him quickly and painlessly.)
9. Molim vas da ne *ubijete* ovu ideju pre nego što čujete celu moju priču. (Please don't kill this idea before you hear my whole story.)
10. Želeo je da *ubije* svoju dosadu gledajući televiziju. (He wanted to kill his boredom by watching TV.)